cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about improving the accuracy of Single Shot Detectors (SSDs) on object detection by efficiently fusing multi-scale information. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the proposed network topology and architecture simplification techniques may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) research.
